Privacy Policy for Blue Hen Helper

1. Introduction
Welcome to Blue Hen Helper, a custom GPT designed to provide comprehensive information related to the University of Delaware. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information we receive from users of Blue Hen Helper.

2. Information We Collect
a. Personal Information:
We do not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it to us. This may include your name, email address, and any other information you choose to share when contacting us for support or inquiries.

b. Non-Personal Information:
We may collect non-personal information about your interaction with Blue Hen Helper. This includes:
   - Usage data: Information on how you use the service, such as the types of queries you submit.
   - Device data: Information about the device you use to access Blue Hen Helper, including IP address, browser type, and operating system.

3. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information for the following purposes:
   - To provide and maintain the Blue Hen Helper service.
   - To improve and personalize your experience with Blue Hen Helper.
   - To analyze usage patterns and improve the functionality and content of Blue Hen Helper.
   - To communicate with you in response to your inquiries and support requests.

4. Disclosure of Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. However, we may disclose your information in the following circumstances:
   - To comply with legal obligations or respond to lawful requests from public authorities.
   - To protect and defend the rights or property of Blue Hen Helper.
   - To prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing in connection with the service.
   - With your consent or at your direction.

5. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no internet or email transmission is ever fully secure or error-free. Please take special care in deciding what information you send to us.

6. Third-Party Links
Blue Hen Helper may contain links to third-party websites or services that are not owned or controlled by us. We have no control over, and assume no responsibility for, the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites or services.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.

8. Consent
By using Blue Hen Helper, you consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
